Your soul is bound to the Solitary Rose: The
Alone. "When I wake up alone, the shades are still
drawn on the cold window pane so they cast
their lines on my bed and lines on my
face." The Solitary Rose is associated with loneliness,
melancholy, and patience. It is governed by
the goddess Merope and its sign is The Sword,
or Unrequited Love. As a Solitary Rose, you may be summed up as a
hopeless romantic. You desire love and have so
much love to give, but thing just never seem to
work out the way you want them to. In life,
you can be very optomistic, even when things
are gray and nothing works out to your
expectations.

What Rose Is Your Soul Bound To?

So whats it like laying beside a girl thats always broken hearted?
A girl that knows when she dies her pain will live on
Throw her spirit and her soul that will never be aloud a peaceful sleep
A girls who's heart is black from the pain she once numbed out

 So whats it like laying beside a girl who finds peace in solitude?
A girl who prefers the company of herself because of what they once did to her
Although her sleep is not peaceful she carries on
A girl who's cat is her only friend cause she blocked everyone else out

So whats it like laying beside a girl who will never die?
Though her body may grow old and wrinkle, she was sentenced to an eternity
A girl who was born into a peaceful family but was old enough to watch it die
So what it like laying beside me, A girl just doing her time while she waits to be freed?

Awwww...I'm not sure just how to explain how I feel right now. But I think I'm in luv. I'm not sure if its a good thing or not. What if hes just playing with me. Dan said a few things last night. I don't know if hes for real or not. I asked him to tell me something new hes said ... "I want to marry you. Oh wait that not new". He also went to bed then came back. We alway joke about how hes gonna kidnap me. Then he said he Luv's me. He caught me of gard. so It took me a few minutes to reply... I remember thinking the night before "I could so easily fall in Luv with him". I said "think I luv you too". Either, I'm really stupid and and hes really cruel. Or I'm blind and he really in Luv. I'm scared to just give in. I'm really damaged, from past relationships. But I really can picture my self curling up in his arms every morning, for the rest of my life. It feels really nice to be talking to him again. I geuss only time will sort this one out for me.
